INFO:

The Legend of Spyro.: A New Beginning explores the true origins of Spyro 
as you embark on a dangerous, combat-driven quest that will bring you face 
to face with the Dark Master.s ultimate creation, Cynder. Experience the 
true power of the purple dragon as you unleash devastating fury attacks, 
upgradeable breaths & ground to aerial melee combos in a frenzied battle 
with hordes of menacing enemies and bone-chilling bosses. This epic and 
cinematic gameplay experience also harnesses the voice talent of 
Hollywood.s best.
